    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sloping channels for the transfer of clothes and linens requiring laundering from upper floors to laundry rooms located on lower floors, either in a home or commercial hotel.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
